# Development Setup and Workflows

## Docker Configuration
- [compose.yaml](mdc:compose.yaml) - Docker Compose configuration
- [.dockerignore](mdc:.dockerignore) - Docker ignore patterns
- `.docker/compose` - Docker Compose overrides and configurations

## Development Scripts
- [Makefile](mdc:Makefile) - Common development commands
- [scripts](mdc:scripts) - Helper scripts directory

## Configuration Files
- [.env.example](mdc:.env.example) - Environment variables template
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - UI components configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration
- [prettier.config.js](mdc:prettier.config.js) - Code formatting rules

## CI/CD
- [.github/workflows](mdc:.github/workflows) - GitHub Actions workflows

## Development Guidelines
1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and configure environment variables
2. Use `make` commands for common development tasks
3. Follow TypeScript strict mode guidelines
4. Ensure ESLint and Prettier rules pass before committing
5. Use Docker Compose for local development environment
